data.description: You can't beat one level living on nearly an acre of land! This freshly renovated, move-in ready home has all you need complete with beautiful mountain views you can enjoy from your front porch or back deck. The spacious primary suite has a bonus room that can be used for anything your heart desires- office, sitting room, let your imagination run wild! Right outside of it, you'll find an oversized living room and large kitchen with new appliances. Opposite the primary suite, there are two other bedrooms and a large bathroom. The home is on a permanent foundation, has a new roof and new water heater. Yard barn in back does convey. Call your favorite Realtor and see this one today!
